{"tid":1275253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知大家有冇miss到晏晝兩點一件事","createTime":"2019-07-01T18:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T02:21:30.000Z","uid":141072,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4d84a17a335fda17a1697a2f373d612774e75cbf","tid":1275253,"uid":141072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:44:53.000Z","msg":"用鐵籠車啱啱撞開玻璃下面既時候，有人（我唔知係鬼係人定係入面既警犬）摻咗一大揸石灰粉喺玻璃入面。當然，咁樣好成功令到警察散退咗幾分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但，好多手足都被tk到</span></span>，我唔知係大家唔為意定咩，但我對手真係灸燒到幾痛下。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知點解在場、同埋跟住幾個鐘內因為掂到其他人衣物、背囊上面既石灰粉而灸傷既人冇出聲。我只係知我忍到痛既同時，<span style=\"color: red;\">聽到有好多因為燒到好痛而去first aid</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家要知道石灰粉最有效率只能夠用油去清洗，而在場係冇可能有油、亦且唔會有人鍾意全身都要被淋油。</span><br />\n<br />\n我見唔到有其他post講依件事，<span style=\"color: red;\">但如果係自己人放既話，真係好重要，一定要保證唔好摻到去手足既衣物、更加要保證唔好摻到去自己人既身體上，先至好用</span>，而以我個人經歷去講，我覺得石灰粉無論係攻擊定防守都好有用。<br />\n<br />\n以下留言開放有份中招既圍爐區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544f29fd821db4399510a0ac358ca686c6c91a9f","tid":1275253,"uid":34742,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:45:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5165da2b4d53f1f31d6a9a5eec872066dc7cc76","tid":1275253,"uid":247905,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:46:32.000Z","msg":"我係feel到隻手有少少輕微曬傷左既feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為真係曬親<br />\n<br />\n今日去左赤柱游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc7add826e2c8c0d34ef1a965893fc21f7f68ba","tid":1275253,"uid":141072,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a5165da2b4d53f1f31d6a9a5eec872066dc7cc76","tid":1275253,"uid":247905,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:46:32.000Z","msg":"我係feel到隻手有少少輕微曬傷左既feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為真係曬親<br />\n<br />\n今日去左赤柱游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:50:16.000Z","msg":"我一開始都唔知咩事，後來諗返，石灰粉一定好易可以由空氣傳播，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最慘係個痛楚至少會持續半個鐘以上</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d677f30b58f04fff84c2d2c335931e13fa275d","tid":1275253,"uid":69746,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90202a0eb77b4a0b2ee44560c75d6be352fca0f3","tid":1275253,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:54:48.000Z","msg":"...希望del 到post"},{"pid":"4f321feb22a9f17e25d4a10bf10c24c75cb03c80","tid":1275253,"uid":69525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:56:53.000Z","msg":"你個夢咁真既"},{"pid":"d67d0334c1663cdc0636e9655940e060ecb08446","tid":1275253,"uid":267953,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:00:31.000Z","msg":"樓主又發夢喇"},{"pid":"dff85da1620f887b1628014e109528ffe604b8a5","tid":1275253,"uid":156666,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90202a0eb77b4a0b2ee44560c75d6be352fca0f3","tid":1275253,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:54:48.000Z","msg":"...希望del 到post"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:01:49.000Z","msg":"發夢姐"},{"pid":"b099f8e4b8f690c97c1b22a4767b885020cbce01","tid":1275253,"uid":156666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dff85da1620f887b1628014e109528ffe604b8a5","tid":1275253,"uid":156666,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90202a0eb77b4a0b2ee44560c75d6be352fca0f3","tid":1275253,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:54:48.000Z","msg":"...希望del 到post"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:01:49.000Z","msg":"發夢姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:02:13.000Z","msg":"識樓主真人 佢話打漏左"},{"pid":"c4f53f20a6ffdf